title: Bad Cameo
description: I loved lets start here and just generally the sounds yachty has been going for lately. him pairing up with james blake works very well and they made a great album. would love to listen to this on a late nite walk looking at the stars.

title: 4 Your Eyez Only
description: I'm not much of a Cole fan generally, but I revisted this record and its really good. I dont see it get talked about that much so def check it out or revisit it if its been a while. probably my favorite Cole album.
